    <item>
      <title>墨西哥总统谢因鲍姆公布减少谋杀案的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/sheinbaum-unveils-plan-to-reduce-murders-that-surged-under-amlo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆呼吁加强情报工作，遏制暴力犯罪，她的前任在位期间，墨西哥经历了近代史上最血腥的时期之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/sheinbaum-unveils-plan-to-reduce-murders-that-surged-under-amlo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 19:27:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦向因土地掠夺而受益的农民提供土地使用权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/zimbabwe-gives-tenure-to-farmers-who-benefitted-from-land-grabs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位内阁部长表示，二十多年前因土地征用而受益的津巴布韦黑人农民将把他们的 99 年租约转为土地使用权，从而允许他们出售土地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/zimbabwe-gives-tenure-to-farmers-who-benefitted-from-land-grabs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 19:09:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
